! Initial revision
!
! Note:
! January 20, 2010: We experienced a problem in upgrading Warehouse from V3.0 to V4.0.
!                   The R value of the semiheated roof goes to around 0.0002 for Miami and Ryihad which V4.0 compliants that it is below 0.001.
!                   This was not a problem for V3.0.  Here we implemented a temporal solution to re-set the r value to 0.001 when it is below it.
! ------------------------------------------------------------------
!
