    SumOrAverage,            !- Aggregation Type for Variable or Meter 1
    Heating:NaturalGas,      !- Variable or Meter 2 Name
    SumOrAverage;            !- Aggregation Type for Variable or Meter 2

  Output:Table:Monthly,
